-- 1. DALL-E 3 - OpenAI image-gen head-term, peer-double for midjourney/firefly/stable-diffusion S184/leonardo S164/flux S165
('dall-e-3', 'DALL-E 3',
'OpenAI image model embedded in ChatGPT and the API for natural-language image generation.',
'DALL-E 3 is the third generation image model from OpenAI, originally released in October 2023 and continuously updated since. It is the image generator embedded inside ChatGPT (free tier with daily limits, unlimited on Plus and Team), available via the OpenAI API at roughly 4 to 8 cents per image depending on resolution, and the default backend when Microsoft Designer or Bing Image Creator generate images. The defining trait vs Midjourney and Stable Diffusion is prompt adherence: DALL-E 3 reads long natural-language descriptions and renders the exact composition asked for, including legible text inside images and correct spatial relationships, with much less prompt engineering than competitors require. Style flexibility is broad (photorealistic, illustrated, vector, painted, 3D render) but the model is less tuned for the hyper-aesthetic stylized output that Midjourney specialists prefer. Content policy is the strictest of major image generators: no public figures, no copyrighted characters, strict on violence and adult content. For non-technical users who want one image right from a paragraph of description rather than iterating a short prompt, DALL-E 3 stays the lowest-friction pick in 2026.',
'', 'https://openai.com/index/dall-e-3', 'https://openai.com/index/dall-e-3',
'freemium', true, 20, 4.5, 5800,
false, false, false,
ARRAY['image-ai', 'ai-assistants'],
ARRAY['Best in class prompt adherence on long descriptive prompts',
'Embedded in ChatGPT so non-technical users access it without a separate app',
'Renders legible text inside images much more reliably than Midjourney v6',
'API access at 4 to 8 cents per image scales for product use cases',
'Strict content policy reduces brand-safety risk for enterprise teams'],
ARRAY['Less aesthetic out of the box than Midjourney v7 stylized output',
'Strict content policy blocks public figures and many creative use cases',
'No batch generation, grid view, or seed reuse like Midjourney',
'Style consistency across a series of images is weaker than Leonardo or Flux',
'Pricing inside ChatGPT Plus is uncapped only for Team and Enterprise seats'],
ARRAY['One-shot images from natural-language descriptions for blog posts and slides',
'Product mockups and concept art for non-designer founders',
